_header: O Lord by whom all thing is wrought
Subjects: hymns, to Christ; Christ, hymns to
_description: James Ryman, a hymn to Christ — six stanzas rhyme royal

CULEe112.First Lines:
O lorde by whome alle thing is wroughtAnd without whome is wrought
                    nothyng…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…And defende vs fro endeles wooAnd fro the fende oure goostly
                    foo
